Vol / Page:  272
Edition:
Quote:  Blue tussock (<i>Poa colensoi</i> and <i>Poa intermedia</i>) grow about 8 inches high with bluish narrow leaves. The only palatable tussocks are, (1) the blue tussocks which are easily killed by continuous burning and by continuous close grazing..
