Edition:
Quote:  From the Gorge Creek to Gow's Creek, right back to the main range, the alpine country will in summer time carry a sheep to the acre, and this upon the best fattening native grasses and herbs, blue tussock, soft speargrass, aniseed, and cotton plant.
